QuestData.Title: Thieving Little Monsters!
QuestData.Description: The long stretch of coastline directly south of our position that extends from west to east is known as the Western Strand. Along the Western Strand you will find two things: murlocs and our stolen "supplies."$B$B<Keyton puts his hands in the air and makes quotation marks with his fingers.>$B$BThose damned thieving murlocs struck while our backs were turned and took our "supplies."$B$BSarus and I cannot leave this post. We need you to head to the Western Strand and recover those "supplies!"
QuestData.RewardText: At least we'll be prepared for any future incidents. Moving "supplies" like this around is a risky proposition. You never know who is going to open their big fat mouth.$B$B<Keyton raises what appears to be an eyebrow at you.>
